---
title: Crumbed Chicken Strips & Garlic Veggies with Zesty Mayo
description: You think you know crumbed chicken? Think again! With our Aussie spice blend in the mix, it goes from tasty to
totally irresistible. Paired with a nutritious assortment of vegetables and zesty mayo for extra creamy deliciousness,
you'll be talking about this long after you've scooped up the final crumbs.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
